    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think the `value` should be the value provided as argument in the CALL. There can be only two cases: either the call was successfull and `value` was transferred, or teh call was unsuccessfull and `0` was tranferred. \r\n\r\nI don't know how to consider selfdestruct. There is no `value` in the suicide op, the suicide op only has a beneficiary. So semantically it shouldn't be there, but I understand that it would be practical...",
